==English==

===Alternative spellings=== 

meta-puzzle

===Etymology===

[[meta-]] (in the transcending, transforming and self-referential senses) + [[puzzle]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{{1|A metapuzzle is a puzzle that combines other puzzles to create a compound puzzle. In contrast to a regular puzzle, a metapuzzle is missing data that is essential to solving it, and which can only be obtained by solving other sometimes entirely unrelated puzzles. Metapuzzles are frequently used in [[puzzlehunt|puzzlehunts]]}}}. A metametapuzzle (also written meta-meta-puzzle) is a metapuzzle that requires the solutions to other metapuzzles in order to be solved.

